title: Smart Jalapeño Popper Turkey Bake with Green Beans and Carrots
description: This low-starch supper is loaded with restaurant-worthy flavour! Tender turkey bites are covered in delicious cheesy and spicy jalapeño goodness. A pile of roasted veggies comes on the side for good measure.

